---
// Disciplines component for CrossFit and Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu
---

<section id="disciplines" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="overline">Disciplinas</div>
    <h2 class="h2">Entrena con los mejores</h2>

    <div class="disciplines-grid">
      <article class="card discipline-card">
        <div class="discipline-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill="#ff6a2a" d="M12 2 2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5Z"></path>
            <path fill="#ff6a2a" d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="h3">CrossFit</h3>
        <p>
          Entrenamiento funcional de alta intensidad que combina fuerza,
          acondicionamiento y movilidad. Metodología escalable para todos los
          niveles con coaching experto.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card discipline-card">
        <div class="discipline-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              fill="#ff6a2a"
              d="M12 1a9 9 0 1 0 .001 18.001A9 9 0 0 0 12 1Zm1 5h-2v6h6v-2h-4V6Z"
            ></path>
            <path
              fill="#ff6a2a"
              d="M17 14h-2v2h2v-2zm-4 0h-2v2h2v-2zm-4 0H7v2h2v-2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="h3">Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu</h3>
        <p>
          Arte marcial y sistema de defensa personal enfocado en técnica y
          estrategia. Dirigido por Vanessa Vargas, segunda cinta negra del país
          y campeona internacional.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .disciplines-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .discipline-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .discipline-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .discipline-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .discipline-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .discipline-card p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .discipline-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .discipline-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .discipline-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #ff6a2a;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .disciplines-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .discipline-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
